{"tid":1495732,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"823 823 823 紅藍綠三線和你牽","createTime":"2019-08-22T07:42:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T09:58:21.000Z","uid":306114,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"cbe98880b717844ba2ad7016709f7ae0a114bdef","tid":1495732,"uid":306114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T07:42:26.000Z","msg":"正式名稱：<br />\n<strong>《香港之路 The Hong Kong Way》</strong><br />\n日期：2019年8月23日（星期五）<br />\n時間：7-9pm<br />\n1900 在指定集合點外集合<br />\n2000 自發手牽手形成香港之路<br />\n2100 流水式散去<br />\n集合地點：#港島線 #荃灣線 #觀塘線 指定港鐵站<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">請集中三線</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>‼注意事項‼</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1) 無特定Dresscode<br />\n2) 聽到熟悉既歌曲 (如Do you hear the people sing) 邀請各位大大聲一齊唱<br />\n3) 有航拍機飛過嘅時候請開起電flashlight<br />\n(怕唔方便舉電話既可以自備螢光棒 頭燈等發光物品)<br />\n4) 馬路 唔方便企人位 可以以雷射筆連起 但唔係個個有 義工都另外準備左d絲帶<br />\n5) 各位注意安全 參加者和平理性非暴力 不作出任何違法行為 遇上重大危險人鏈會解散及離開</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<ins>Links</ins><br />\n823 香港之路頻道<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><a href=\"https://t.me/HKWay\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKWay&d=MOEBQbH5BhSBv0g7AWUGIQKEBJewdHKi9Ib5gSSGE6s%3D&h=dd13e647\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HKWay</a></span><br />\n<br />\n823 香港之路公海群組<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/J3VqxBTMg_LTNL9idzQLOw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FJ3VqxBTMg_LTNL9idzQLOw&d=MOEBQbH5BhSBv0g7AWUGIQKEBJewdHKi9Ib5gSSGE6s%3D&h=ccc2efa8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/J3VqxBTMg_LTNL9idzQLOw</a></span><br />\n <br />\n路線地圖<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/d/u/1/viewer?mid=1epO7dqTyWkTGVD1qqStYdUdKnsdboBcZ&amp;ll=22.32288133674603%2C114.18210443909493&amp;z=13\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fmaps%2Fd%2Fu%2F1%2Fviewer%3Fmid%3D1epO7dqTyWkTGVD1qqStYdUdKnsdboBcZ%26ll%3D22.32288133674603%252C114.18210443909493%26z%3D13&d=MOEBQbH5BhSBv0g7AWUGIQKEBJewdHKi9Ib5gSSGE6s%3D&h=c1a9b643\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/maps/d/u/1/viewer?mid=1epO7dqTyWkTGVD1qqStYdUdKnsdboBcZ&amp;ll=22.32288133674603%2C114.18210443909493&amp;z=13</a></span><br />\n<br />\nFacebook<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/香港之路-The-Hong-Kong-Road-100523197988108/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%B9%8B%E8%B7%AF-The-Hong-Kong-Road-100523197988108%2F&d=MOEBQbH5BhSBv0g7AWUGIQKEBJewdHKi9Ib5gSSGE6s%3D&h=55c9370f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/香港之路-The-Hong-Kong-Road-100523197988108/</a></span><br />\n<br />\nInstagram<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><a href=\"https://instagram.com/hkway823\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fhkway823&d=MOEBQbH5BhSBv0g7AWUGIQKEBJewdHKi9Ib5gSSGE6s%3D&h=5ec6c7c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/hkway823</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/McVZfva.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMcVZfva.jpg&h=1a9291e3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"99a25d45a4101fbad3a671336c235b9829ff0929","tid":1495732,"uid":306114,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T07:43:56.000Z","msg":"<strong><ins>Q &amp; A</ins></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nQ1. 我去邊都得, 點知邊度缺人?<br />\nA1. TG channel會用嚟作即時發佈~ <a href=\"https://t.me/HKWay\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKWay&d=MOEBQbH5BhSBv0g7AWUGIQKEBJewdHKi9Ib5gSSGE6s%3D&h=dd13e647\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HKWay</a><br />\n<br />\nQ2. 馬路點連?<br />\nA2. 不阻塞交通 綠燈連 又或者用創意既手法連~ 又或者唔連~ Be Water!<br />\n<br />\nQ3. 開手機燈點拖手?<br />\nA3. 大家一齊右手拎手機 左手拖住隔離既人既右手~<br />\n<br />\nQ4. 幾時要開燈?<br />\nA4. 覺得差唔多形成人鏈就開得啦~<br />\n<br />\nQ5. 會唔會有路線圖?<br />\nA5. 我地一有確實既路線圖就會公佈google map link俾大家~<br />\n<br />\nQ6. 有無dress code?<br />\nA6. 無dress code~ 擔心會落雨既人士可以帶傘~<br />\n<br />\nQ7. 除左文宣果三條線外 其他路線係咪你地有份搞?<br />\nA7. 係其他網民自發搞既<br />\n<br />\nQ8. 係咪一定要7點到?<br />\nA8. 組成人鏈需時都需要熱心既你地幫手! 多你一個多好多~ 希望大家可以7點到! 唔能夠7點到既都歡迎到時加入架!!!<br />\n<br />\nQ9. 我果區無集合點/路線 我可以去邊?<br />\nA9. 麻煩留意Tg channel 邊度唔夠人就去邊度~ 或者3條線隨便去一個位~<br />\n<br />\nQ10. 係咪會有人影相?<br />\nA10. 呢個活動既目的之一係想俾全世界都望到香港發生咩事~ 關注香港~ 我地歡迎媒體，熱心市民同埋好奇街坊影相~"},{"pid":"67893641153b14b909b059fc7681108590f1fcaa","tid":1495732,"uid":103102,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T07:46:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u1ZOTim.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu1ZOTim.jpg&h=79b0a6b9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4b207fb2f9723434d51f178aea993059753ee443","tid":1495732,"uid":306114,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T08:00:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8o4OTnY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8o4OTnY.jpg&h=d81a958a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bUOjZ20.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbUOjZ20.jpg&h=f71830ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cbd20c658fc83a1c2c270b0b8f4a40d67e62543","tid":1495732,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T08:22:00.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">莫洛托夫&mdash;里賓特洛甫條約</span><br />\nvs <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">中英聯合聲明</span></span></strong><br />\n我係咪看見突破<img src=\"/a